title: Clifford-Simak.rar
description:
Clifford D. Simak Compilation

All the novels (26, City as one file) plus 109 of the short stories.

The illustrations (covers as well as interior artwork) are from magazines. Format, html/css and jpg/png. About two dozen shorts were added.

A full list of Simak's novels and short stories (about 115) can be found at www.isfdb.org. 

The following shorts are missing:

'I Had No Head and My Eyes Were Floating Way Up In the Air'. 
The Western Stories ('Gunsmoke Interlude', 'Barb Wire Brings Bullets', 'Way for the Hangtown Rebel', 'Trail City's Hot-Lead Crusaders'.)
'No More Hides and Tallow'.

'Byte Your Tongue' and 'Limiting Factor', non English version only.

Review folder: A small collection of secondary literature on Simak
